      <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:#a8a29e;line-height:1.6;">School catchment boundaries: Queensland Government My School catchment lookup at <a href="https://catchments.education.qld.gov.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#c4912a;">catchments.education.qld.gov.au</a>. Catchment boundaries are subject to change. Always confirm the current catchment for your property before marketing. School names and catchment areas referenced in this article reflect the position as at 2026. Private school enrolment criteria are set by each school independently and proximity does not confer priority.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</article>
